---
title: Tandoori Chicken & Roast Kumara Bowl with Garlic Yoghurt Dressing
description: Bowls are all the rage right now... Buddha bowls, poke bowls, and now a tandoori chicken bowl. In keeping with the theme, this is healthy while still being incredibly satisfying, warming and aromatic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bc521ca30006c33fa5eb9d2-56e01244.jpg
